---
title: French-Inspired Lentil Salad with Herby Goat Cheese and Walnuts
description: Satisfying and sophisticated, this vegetarian salad makes a superb supper! Marinated lentils provide a hearty salad base and creamy, tangy goat cheese is rolled in fresh herbs for a luxurious topping!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/salade-de-lentilles-a-la-francaise-ab3681a0.jpg
